{"tid":1280624,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一日複一日我好攰","createTime":"2019-07-03T04:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T05:29:24.000Z","uid":134844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb94c793ebff55d42e58df99ee7c429b9f60bd52","tid":1280624,"uid":134844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:47:14.000Z","msg":"由開始考final開始個人開始想摺埋，乜人都唔想理唔想做好想接埋自己，好想消失。<br />\n仲要睇到香港變到咁真係好絕望。雖然話自己拎歐洲passport 但始終係香港大，香港係我屋企。<br />\n仲要早幾日比個朋友全面封鎖，話佢好攰幫我唔到。其實好似人話變就變咁，當然我知自己都好有問題唔係點解會冇乜朋友。日日都同自己講自己過得好好，唔好死亦唔可以死。<br />\n但我真係好攰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23991ddbc043adfe103c0fe58eba303879e1885","tid":1280624,"uid":200483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:51:41.000Z","msg":"加油 攰就真係要俾啲時間自己休息吓 唔好接觸相關資訊住<br />\n<br />\n呢條路點都要行 但你可以決定點樣行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167c58b2841ef9aa99bf90a0ec56122b470f8c3d","tid":1280624,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"有後路已經好過好多人<br />\n<br />\n專心考試先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c729981085be8035ec120b41b8462ae08a31c0","tid":1280624,"uid":134844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"167c58b2841ef9aa99bf90a0ec56122b470f8c3d","tid":1280624,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"有後路已經好過好多人<br />\n<br />\n專心考試先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"其實我5月尾就考完。<br />\n只不過我係個圈到出唔返嚟"},{"pid":"fcd201961b938c17321436